🤖 Understanding AI Agents
An AI agent is not a chatbot.
A chatbot answers questions.
An agent completes objectives.
Every agent follows a loop:
```text
Perceive
 ↓
Plan
 ↓
Act
 ↓
Observe
 ↓
Iterate
```
Five Components of Every Agent
1. Model
The reasoning engine.
2. Tools
External capabilities.
Examples:
APIs
Databases
Browsers
Code execution
Search systems
3. Memory
Stores information across tasks.
4. Orchestration
Coordinates workflows.
5. Deployment
Makes the system available in production.
Mental Model
```text
Chatbot = Answers

Agent = Works
```
