⚡ Vibe Coding vs Agentic Engineering
Vibe Coding
Characteristics:
Natural language instructions
Fast iteration
Minimal verification
Great for experimentation
Example:
```text
Build a dashboard for customer analytics.
```
The AI generates code.
The developer checks whether it works.
This approach is excellent for:
MVPs
Internal tools
Personal projects
Hackathons
Agentic Engineering
Agentic Engineering introduces structure.
Components:
Architecture documents
Specifications
Automated testing
CI/CD pipelines
Evaluation systems
Monitoring
Human review
Comparison
Area	Vibe Coding	Agentic Engineering
Speed	High	Moderate
Reliability	Low	High
Testing	Minimal	Automated
Verification	Manual	Systematic
Production Ready	Rarely	Yes
Scale	Limited	High
Rule of Thumb
```text
Prototype with Vibe Coding.
Scale with Agentic Engineering.
```
