🏗 Harness Engineering
One of the most important concepts in the paper is Harness Engineering.
The model is not the system.
The surrounding infrastructure determines reliability.
A Production Harness Includes
Automated tests
Evaluations
CI/CD
Monitoring
Logging
Security controls
Memory systems
Retrieval systems
Key Formula
```text
Strong Harness + Average Model
>
Strong Model + Weak Harness
```
Many organizations overinvest in models and underinvest in systems.
The best teams build robust engineering environments around AI.
